PHP-Functions-Mail version 0.01
===============================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Net::SMTP
  Jcode for mb_send_mail function

